comments: Harris (DEN) grabs Leonard's (LAC) arm on the perimeter.
After receiving the inbound pass, Murray (DEN) lifts his pivot foot prior to releasing his dribble.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in George's (LAC) path and gives him a step to avoid the contact.
George (LAC) and Jokic (DEN) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Williams (LAC) and Grant (DEN) engage and separate off ball in the post.
Williams (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Grant's (DEN) path and makes slight contact as they disengage.
Zubac (LAC) makes marginal contact with Jokic (DEN) while rebounding.
George (LAC) makes marginal contact with Jokic (DEN) off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Jokic (DEN) cleanly dislodges the ball from George (LAC) prior to making incidental contact to his side in the backcourt.
Porter (DEN) makes contact with the ball during Zubac's (LAC) shot attempt. Any ensuing contact is deemed incidental.
Morris Sr. (LAC) commits a take foul on Porter Jr. (DEN) after the rebound.
George (LAC) commits a take foul on Morris (DEN).
Jokic (DEN) briefly grasps and releases Zubac's (LAC) arm off ball.
Beverley (LAC) makes contact with Porter Jr.'s (DEN) body at the start of his drive to the basket affecting his SQBR.
Murray (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Beverley's (LAC) path and gives him a step to avoid the contact.
Craig (DEN) makes A to B contact with George (LAC) during his shot attempt.
George (LAC) makes contact to Porter's (DEN) arm during his shot attempt.
